msgstr "Zaten var. Üzerine yazmak ister misiniz?"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"This is the new standard mode of %(gamename)s. Use your left and right "
"arrows to move to the same position as an enemy and spacebar to punch! But "
"remember, they need to be close enough to be hit by your fist. Compared to "
"the previous version, you get bonus points when leveling up. Also, you have "
"chances to get bonuses if you achieve more than 5 consecutive hits!"
msgstr ""
"Bu %(gamename)s oyununun yeni standart modudur. Sağ ve sol okları kullanarak "
"bir düşmanla aynı yöne gelin e boşluk tuşuyla onu yumruklayın! Düşmanın "
"yumruk mesafeniz dahilinde olması gerektiğini unutmayın! Eski sürüme nazaran "
"seviyeniz artınca puan alırsınız. Ayrıca 5 kez art arda düşman "
"yumruklarsanız bonus alma şansınız vardır!"

#, python-format
msgid ""
"This is the new arcade mode of %(gamename)s! From the new version, items "
"that fall faster are more likely to be good, and slower ones are more likely "
"to be bad. You can obtain an item by punching it, or destroy it by combining "
"your up arrow when punching. Carefully choose which item to obtain!"
msgstr ""
"Bu %(gamename)s oyununun yeni arkeyd modudur! Bu yeni sürümde, hızlı düşen "
"bonusların olumlu, yavaş düşen bonusların ise olumsuz etki etme ihtimali "
"daha yüksektir. Bonusu yumruklayarak alabilirsiniz, ya da yukarı okla "
"beraber yumruklarsanız parçalayabilirsiniz. Alacağınız bonusu dikkatli seçin!"

msgid ""
"This is the old-fashioned game mode! You don't get bonuses based on "
"accuracy, so you can punch, punch, punch punch punch and punch! This mode "
"has a sharper levelup curb, meaning that you can collect screams really fast!"
msgstr ""
"Bu klasik oyun modudur! İsabet oranınıza göre bonus almazsınız, bu yüzden "
"sağa sola istediğiniz kadar yumruk sallayabilirsiniz! Bu modda daha hızlı "
"seviye atlarsınız, bu da daha fazla çığlık toplayacağınız anlamına gelir!"

msgid ""
"Welcome to this new and exciting burden mode! In this mode, every item gives "
"you a nasty effect, and each nasty effect boosts points you gain! Guess "
"what? The more you torture yourself, the more point boost you get! Oh, but "
"if you die because of your own torturous act, hahahahahaha, you stupid! Good "
"luck!"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Welcome to chaos mode, where nothing is fair! Every enemy you defeat drops "
"an item, on top of the regular item rain. Falling speed tells you nothing "
"anymore: good and bad items are completely random. There is no accuracy "
"bonus here; instead, grabbing any item, good or bad, earns you points, while "
"letting one hit the ground costs you, and smashing one with your up arrow "
"costs you double! And the destruction item? It now flips a coin for each "
"item, obtaining or destroying it, and the enemies it clears rain down even "
"more items. Embrace the chaos!"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Welcome to Yolo mode, a zero-player autoplay of chaos! Sit back and listen: "
"a bot takes over, moving and punching for you. It always hits the nearest "
"target, prioritizing enemies, chasing the destruction item, collecting good "
"items and smashing bad ones. You don't need to touch the keyboard. Just "
"enjoy the show!"
msgstr ""

